### Problem10

Look at the following Java code (part):

```java
String x ="201";
System.out.println("CS201"=="CS"+x);
System.out.println("CS201"=="CS"+"201");
```

The output of the program will be:

_____(0)\___

_____(1)\___.

Hint: This problem is modified from 'Q&A(Strings)'.
